le, slowly\ngrowing warps could account for the large reflection strengths and absorbing\ncolumn densities inferred late in the 4U 1820-30 and 4U 1636-53 superbursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2022 21:04:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
