 to attak this conjecture.\nThis approach may also help to resolve another labeling conjecture on trees by\nGraham and Sloane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2022 06:14:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
