des the optimal IK solution with respect to the manipulability and the\ncloseness to the current robot configuration. Monte Carlo simulations show the\neffectiveness of the proposed approach which is accurate and real-time capable\n($\\approx$ \\SI{32}{\\micro\\second}) on the KUKA LBR iiwa 14 R820.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2022 14:31:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Mar 2023 22:30:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 26 Mar 2023 17:33:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
